g as a dumb user; there are only dumb products.</p>"}],"speaker_name":"Timothy Prestero","tags":["TEDx","design","health care","product design"],"title":"Design for people, not awards","video_type":{"id":"2","name":"TEDx Talk"},"viewed_count":1044287}]}
